'''卡雅·蘿絲·斯考达里奥-戴維斯'''（{{lang-en|Kaya Rose Scodelario-Davis}}，{{bd|1992年|3月13日|catIdx=S}}）是一位[[英格兰|英格兰]][[女演员|女演员]]，在[[E4_(電視頻道)|E4]]青少年剧《[[皮囊|皮囊]]》中扮演{{link-en|艾菲·史通|Effy Stonem}}而成名。

==早年生活==
斯考达里奥的母亲是[[意大利|意大利]]裔[[巴西人|巴西人]]，1990年移居[[英国|英国]]，父亲是[[英格兰|英格兰]]人。<ref>"Britain's Got Talent", ''The Sunday Times Magazine'', 25 January 2009, page 5. http://www.imagebam.com/image/50aa3045509301/ {{Wayback|url=http://www.imagebam.com/image/50aa3045509301/ |date=20200915071154 }} (Scanned image) "Half Brazilian, fluent in Portuguese and stunningly attractive"</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://mobile.twitter.com/kScodders/status/7071583084482560?screen_name=kScodders |title=Twitter |publisher=Mobile.twitter.com |date= |accessdate=2013-11-20 |archive-date=2020-09-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200915074816/https://mobile.twitter.com/kScodders/status/7071583084482560?screen_name=kScodders |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author=TV and Radio |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/tvandradio/10139731/Kaya-Scodelario-on-life-after-Skins.html |title=Kaya Scodelario on life after 'Skins' |publisher=Telegraph |date= |accessdate=2013-11-20 |archive-date=2020-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111205101/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/tvandradio/10139731/Kaya-Scodelario-on-life-after-Skins.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>由於父母离婚後跟随母亲生活，所以能说流利的[[葡萄牙语|葡萄牙语]]。<ref>[[Sunday_Telegraph|Sunday Telegraph]], Stella Magazine supplement, January 2010 Issue, page 23.</ref>然而她在童年时曾被霸凌，这使她把演戏當作一種抒發的管道。<ref>[[Katie_Grand|LOVE (Magazine)]], ''The Naughty Little Sister'', page 118.</ref>

== 个人生活 ==
斯考达里奥在接受采访时透露她曾与《皮囊》的演员[[傑克·奧康奈爾_(演員)|傑克·奧康奈爾]]交往一年，於2009年6月分手，但他们仍是好朋友。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.fhm.com/girls/covergirls/kaya-scodelario |title=Kaya Scodelario | Sexy grumpster | Girls We Love |publisher=FHM.com |date= |accessdate=2013-11-20 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131020094051/http://www.fhm.com/girls/covergirls/kaya-scodelario |archivedate=2013-10-20 }}</ref><ref name="naomily.com">[[Company_(magazine)|Company (magazine)]]. [http://www.naomily.com/gallery/displayimage.php?pid=220&fullsize=1 Interview] {{Wayback|url=http://www.naomily.com/gallery/displayimage.php?pid=220&fullsize=1 |date=20110714153145 }} (Scanned image) Quote: "I got linked to Nicholas Hoult when he was in Skins. I was only 14 at the time and played his sister! Just for the record I've never been married to Nick Hoult. I did go out with Jack [who plays Cook] for a year and we were quite open about our relationship in the press."</ref><ref>[http://www.fanpop.com/spots/skins/images/10565050/title/kaya-luke-jack-heat-magazine-photo Heat Interview] {{Wayback|url=http://www.fanpop.com/spots/skins/images/10565050/title/kaya-luke-jack-heat-magazine-photo |date=20120402045831 }}.(Scanned image)</ref>她与[[埃利奥特·提特恩索|埃利奥特·提特恩索]]从2009年开始恋人关系，在2014年初分手。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.thesun.co.uk/sol/homepage/showbiz/tv/2805324/Kaya-Scodelario-has-been-secretly-dating-Shameless-star-Elliott-Tittensor.html |title=Kaya Scodelario has been secretly dating Shameless star Elliott Tittensor |date=2010-01-13 |newspaper=The Sun |accessdate=2011-05-07 |archive-date=2015-06-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150630082740/http://www.thesun.co.uk/sol/homepage/showbiz/tv/2805324/Kaya-Scodelario-has-been-secretly-dating-Shameless-star-Elliott-Tittensor.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2014年4月，她开始与合作的演员[[班傑明·沃克|班傑明·沃克]]交往，于2014年12月28日订婚<ref>{{cite news|url=http://instagram.com/p/xKzb-6qT4c|title=The Happiest Woman in the World|date=2014-12-28|work=@kayascods|accessdate=2018-03-28|archive-date=2019-07-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190726095948/https://www.instagram.com/p/xKzb-6qT4c/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，并于2015年12月结婚。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.people.com/article/benjamin-walker-kaya-scodelario-married|title=Holiday Wedding! Benjamin Walker and Kaya Scodelario Tie the Knot|last=Guglielmi|first=Jodi|date=2016-01-08|publisher=People|accessdate=2018-03-28|archive-date=2016-05-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160520032617/http://www.people.com/article/benjamin-walker-kaya-scodelario-married|dead-url=no}}</ref>他们的儿子出生于2016年11月。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.instagram.com/p/BGW7v0nqTx_/?taken-by=kayascods|title=Instagram photo by Kaya Scodelario-Davis • Jun 7, 2016 at 3:29pm UTC|website=Instagram|access-date=2016-06-07}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.eonline.com/news/813020/benjamin-walker-and-kaya-scodelario-welcome-their-first-child|title=Benjamin Walker and Kaya Scodelario Welcome Their First Child|publisher=|accessdate=2017-02-13|archive-date=2021-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210211221606/http://www.eonline.com/news/813020/benjamin-walker-and-kaya-scodelario-welcome-their-first-child|dead-url=no}}</ref>演员[[丹尼尔·卡卢亚|丹尼尔·卡卢亚]]是孩子的教父。<ref>{{Citation|last=Filmlounge|title=MAZE RUNNER 3 Interview with Dylan O' Brien, Kaya Scodelario, Thomas Brodie-Sangster & Wes Ball|date=2018-01-27|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7zx38bJQjyQ|accessdate=2018-02-01|archive-date=2022-02-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220214060147/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7zx38bJQjyQ|dead-url=no}}</ref>

从2008年到2010年，斯考达里奥独自一人住在伦敦北部，她认为对女性重要的是“独立和坚强”。<ref>[[InStyle|InStyle UK]], ''Urban Jungle'' page 112, July 2009.</ref>斯考达里奥患有[[失讀症|失讀症]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.twitter.com/#!/kayascollywogs/status/2835064756903936|title=Scodelario Tweets About Her Dyslexia|last=Scodelario|first=Kaya|date=2010-11-11|work=@kayascollywogs|accessdate=2014-08-17|archive-date=2011-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110224005300/http://twitter.com/#!/kayascollywogs/status/2835064756903936|dead-url=no}}</ref>她的父亲于2010年11月22日去世。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/#!/kayascollywogs/status/7071583084482560|title=Scodelario Tweets About the Loss of her Father|last=Scodelario|first=Kaya|date=2010-11-23|work=@kayascollywogs|accessdate=2014-08-17|archive-date=2016-07-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160705115332/https://twitter.com/#!/kayascollywogs/status/7071583084482560|dead-url=no}}</ref>她被英国版的FHM评为2010年世界100位最性感女性第13位。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://showbiz.sky.com/fhm-sexiest-women-10/13 |title=FHM: 100 Sexiest Women |publisher=Sky |date=2010-04-29 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100919181127/http://showbiz.sky.com/fhm-sexiest-women-10/13 |archivedate=2010-09-19 |accessdate=2014-08-17 }}</ref>

